escription": null, "English": "I bear witness that there is no god save Allah, alone without having any partner, One and Only and Besought of all. He begets not, nor is He begotten, and there is none comparable to Him.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mai gawahi deta hu keh Allah ke siwa koi ma’bood nahi jo yakta hai koi Uska saani nahi hai, Woh yakta o be-neyaaz hai, na Us ne kisi ko jana, na Woh jana gaya aur na koi Us ka hamsar o saani ho sakta hai.", "Urdu": "میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ اﷲکے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں جو یکتا ہے کوئی اس کا ثانی نہیں ہے وہ یکتا و بے نیاز ہے نہ اس نے کسی کو جنا نہ وہ جنا گیا اور نہ کوئی اس کا ہمسر و ثانی ہو سکتا ہے۔", "RArabic": "ASH-HADO AN LAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO WAHDAHU LAA SHAREEKA LAHU AHADAN SAMADAN LAM YALID WA LAM YOOLAD WA LAM YAKUN LAHU KOFOWAN AHADUN.", "ArabicText1": "اَشْہَدُ اَنْ لَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللهُ وَحْدَہٗ لَا شَرِیْكَ لَہٗ اَحَدًا صَمَدًا لَمْ یَلِدْ وَلَمْ یُوْلَدْ وَلَمْ یَكُنْ لَّہٗ كُفُوًا اَحَدٌ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "Arabic